| list-customers | Print every customer as `<id>  <name>  <email>` |
| add-product | Add a product: `add-product <id> <name> <price>` |
| help | Print all available commands |
```

**Pattern:**
- Markdown table with Command | Description columns
- Usage examples in descriptions
- One row per command
- Convention #8: Every user-facing command must have a row here

